== 生平 ==

=== 早期 ===
童年时期，家境困难的苏木达尔基经常在大山里放牛。因其热爱运动，他在2010年被介绍到[[恩波格斗俱乐部|恩波格斗俱乐部]]开始学习[[散打|散打]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=苏木达尔基UFC三连胜，这个藏族放牛小子野心不小|url=http://www.bjnews.com.cn/detail/161122196615250.html|accessdate=2021-01-22|author=|date=|format=|work=www.bjnews.com.cn|publisher=|language=}}</ref>2016年，苏木达尔基开始职业生涯。他在[[河南卫视|河南卫视]]格斗节目《[[武林笼中对|武林笼中对]]》取得了11胜3负的战绩，并获得蝇量级金腰带冠军。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Su Mudaerji|url=https://www.sherdog.com/fighter/Su-Mudaerji-228263|accessdate=2020-08-07|author=Sherdog.com|work=Sherdog}}</ref>

=== UFC时期 ===
2018年11月24日，作为UFC第一位藏族选手，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Su Mudaerji’s UFC debut is ‘a moment of pride for the people of Tibet’|url=https://www.mmafighting.com/2018/11/23/18108645/su-mudaerji-ufc-debut-moment-pride-people-tibet-beijing|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2018-11-23|last=Cruz|first=Guilherme|work=MMA Fighting|language=en}}</ref>苏木达尔基在UFC格斗之夜141迎来他的首秀，对战路易斯·斯莫卡。苏木达尔基在第二回合被以十字固降服。<ref>{{Cite web|title=UFC Beijing Preliminary Card Results and Recap|url=https://cagesidepress.com/2018/11/24/ufc-beijing-preliminary-card-results-and-recap/|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2018-11-24|last=Staff|work=Cageside Press|language=en-US}}</ref>

2019年8月31日，苏木达尔基在UFC格斗之夜157对战安德烈·苏康塔斯，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Su Mudaerji vs. Andre Soukhamthath toegevoegd aan UFC Shenzhen card|url=https://mmadna.nl/sumudaerji-vs-andre-soukhamthath-toegevoegd-aan-ufc-shenzhen-card/|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2019-07-23|last=DNA|first=MMA|work=MMA DNA|language=en-US}}</ref>最终以一致裁决赢得比赛。<ref>{{Cite web|title=UFC Shenzhen Results: Su Mudaerji Dominates Andre Soukhamthath Impressively|url=https://cagesidepress.com/2019/08/31/ufc-shenzhen-results-su-mudaerji/|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2019-08-31|last=Doherty|first=Dan|work=Cageside Press|language=en-US}}</ref>

2020年11月28日，苏木达尔基在UFC拉斯维加斯15对战马尔科姆·戈登，<ref>{{Cite web|title=Su Mudaerji vs. Malcolm Gordon toegevoegd aan UFC evenement op 28 november|url=https://mmadna.nl/su-mudaerji-vs-malcolm-gordon-toegevoegd-aan-ufc-evenement-op-28-november/|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2020-09-12|last=DNA|first=MMA|work=MMA DNA|language=en-US}}</ref>在第一回合仅用44秒就将其[[擊倒|击倒]]赢得比赛，<ref>{{Cite web|title=UFC Vegas 15 Results: Su Mudaerji Destroys Malcolm Gordon|url=https://cagesidepress.com/2020/11/28/ufc-vegas-15-results-su-mudaerji-destroys-malcolm-gordon/|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2020-11-28|last=Evanoff|first=Josh|work=Cageside Press|language=en-US}}</ref>获得“今夜最佳表现”。<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=UFC Vegas 15 post-fight bonuses: Smith nabs POTN for round 1 triangle|url=https://www.bloodyelbow.com/2020/11/29/21724480/ufc-vegas-15-post-fight-bonuses-smith-nabs-potn-for-first-round-triangle|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2020-11-29|last=Haynes|first=Stephie|work=Bloody Elbow|language=en}}</ref>

2021年1月20日，苏木达尔基在UFC格斗岛8对战扎鲁克·阿达舍夫，并通过一致裁决赢得比赛。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Su Mudaerji pakt short notice partij tegen Zarrukh Adashev op 20 januari in Abu Dhabi|url=https://mmadna.nl/su-mudaerji-pakt-short-notice-partij-tegen-zarrukh-adashev-op-20-januari-in-abu-dhabi/|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2020-12-31|last=DNA|first=MMA|work=MMA DNA|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=UFC Fight Island 8 Results: Su Mudaerji Wins Tactical Fight Over Zarrukh Adashev|url=https://cagesidepress.com/2021/01/20/ufc-fight-island-8-results-su-mudaerji/|accessdate=2021-01-22|date=2021-01-20|last=Doherty|first=Dan|work=Cageside Press|language=en-US}}</ref>此战之后，苏木达尔基进入UFC蝇量级排名第14位。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Rankings - UFC|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127090032/https://www.ufc.com/rankings|accessdate=2021-01-27|author=|date=2021-01-27|format=|work=web.archive.org|publisher=|language=}}</ref>

